content.rendered:
Directed by Tobias Lindholm

Written by Charles Graeber. Krysty Wilson-Cairns

Star Eddie Redmayne(Charlie Cullen). Denise Pillott(Nurse 1). Dartel McRae(Nurse 2). Joseph Fugelo(Dr. Collins). Jessica Chastain(Amy Loughren). Judith Delgado(Ana Martinez). Jesus-Papoleto Melendez(Sam Martinez). Myra Lucretia Taylor(Vivian Neal). Marcia Jean Kurtz(Jackie). Devyn McDowell(Maya Loughren). Alix West Lefler(Alex Loughren). Ajay Naidu(Dr. Robert Hind). Jennean Farmer(Receptionist). Nnamdi Asomugha(Danny Baldwin). Noah Emmerich(Tim Braun). Navya La Shay(Hospital Admin). Kim Dickens(Linda Garran). David Lavine(Duncan Beattie). Bruce MacVittie(Malcolm Burrel). Brooke Stacy Mills(Nurse Hardwick). Charlotte Cohn-Williams(Dr. Moore). Shaun O’Hagan(Prosecutor Ellis). Christine Healy(Assistant (as Christine B. Healy)). Maria Farrow(Dr. Peters). Maurice J. Irvin(Mark Rossi (as Moe Irvin)). Alex Bartner(Messenger). Gabe Fazio(Tom Anderson). Anjelica Bosboom(Kelly Anderson). Malik Yoba(Sam Johnson). Maria Dizzia(Lori Lucas). Rebecca Watson(Nurse Sandra). Jennifer Regan(ER Nurse). Beth Dixon(Diner Waitress). Brian Sayers(State Trooper). Steve Antonucci(Grave digger (uncredited)). Evan Bass(Nurse Geddes (uncredited)). Andrew James Bleidner(Alex Lombardo (uncredited)). David Boston(Driver (uncredited)). Marko Caka(Detective (uncredited)). Chris Henry Coffey(Dr. Steven Reed (uncredited)). Victor Cruz(Gene Smith (uncredited)). Sheetal Deo(Doctor Day Player (uncredited)). Marcia M Francis(Patient (uncredited)). Gina Jun(Doctor (uncredited)). Becca Marks(Night Nurse (uncredited)). Lauren Yaffe(ICU Patient (uncredited))

Language English

Producers Darren Aronofsky. Glen Basner. Ignacio de Medina. Jonathan Filley. Scott Franklin. Ari Handel. Michael Jackman. Josh Stern

Production FilmNation Entertainment. Protozoa Pictures
